msgid "# Stop-ClusterResource"
msgstr "# 停止集群资源"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Takes a resource offline in a failover cluster."
msgstr "在故障转移集群中，将某个资源设置为离线状态。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Stop-ClusterResource` cmdlet takes a resource offline in a failover cluster. Before the\n"
"resource is taken offline, any resources that depend on it are taken offline."
msgstr ""
"`Stop-ClusterResource` cmdlet "
"用于将故障转移集群中的某个资源置于离线状态。在将该资源置为离线状态之前，所有依赖于该资源的资源也会被同时置于离线状态。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Take a resource offline"
msgstr "### 示例 1：将资源置于离线状态"

msgid ""
"This example takes the resource called `IP Address 10.24.11.0` offline on the local cluster.\n"
"Before taking the resource offline, it takes offline any dependent resources."
msgstr ""
"这个示例会将名为“IP Address 10.24.11.0”的资源从本地集群中下线。在将该资源下线之前，系统会先将其所有依赖的资源也一并下线。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定用于运行此cmdlet的集群名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.`或被省略，则cmdlet将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid "Specifies that locked groups are ignored when running the cmdlet."
msgstr "指定在运行该cmdlet时忽略被锁定的组。"

msgid "Specifies the cluster resource to take offline."
msgstr "指定要离线的集群资源。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster resource to take offline. This can also be the name of a Cluster\n"
"Shared Volume."
msgstr "指定要下线的集群资源的名称。这也可以是一个集群共享卷（Cluster Shared Volume）的名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the time in seconds to wait for the cmdlet. If the **Wait** parameter isn't specified,\n"
"then the cmdlet waits for completion. If `-Wait 0` is specified, then the call is initiated and the\n"
"cmdlet returns without waiting."
msgstr ""
"指定命令块需要等待的时间（以秒为单位）。如果未指定 `Wait` 参数，那么命令块会一直等待直到操作完成。如果指定了 `-Wait "
"0`，则命令会立即被执行，而不会等待任何结果，之后命令块会立即返回。"

